選擇是否讓購物車商品連結至單一產品頁面。','Disabled (Recommended)'=>'已停用（建議）','Do not link cart items to single product page. (Recommended)'=>'不要將購物車商品連結至單一產品頁面。（建議）','Enabled'=>'已啟用','Link each cart item to product page.'=>'將每個購物車商品連結至產品頁面。','Open in New Window'=>'在新視窗開啟','Open cart item links in a new window.'=>'在新視窗開啟購物車商品連結。','Cart Item Data Display'=>'購物車商品資料顯示','Choose how to display cart item data.'=>'選擇如何顯示購物車商品資料。','Short (Recommended)'=>'簡短（建議）','Display only variation values. For example, Size: XL, Color: Red is displayed as XL / Red. (Recommended)'=>'僅顯示變體值。例如，尺寸：XL，顏色：紅色顯示為 XL / 紅色。（建議）','WooCommerce Default'=>'WooCommerce 預設','Each variation is displayed on a separate line using this format: Label: Value'=>'每個變體以「標籤：值」格式分行顯示','Store Policies'=>'商店政策','Store Policies are displayed as links in the footer of the checkout, order pay, and thank you pages. Clicking them displays the policy in a modal window.'=>'商店政策會以連結形式顯示於結帳、訂單付款及感謝頁面的頁腳。點擊連結會在彈出視窗中顯示政策內容。','Control the Order Received / Thank You endpoint.'=>'控制訂單已接收 / 謝謝您端點。','Enable Thank You Page Template'=>'啟用謝謝頁面範本','Enable thank you page / order received template.'=>'啟用謝謝頁面 / 訂單已接收範本。','Enable Map Embed'=>'啟用地圖嵌入','Enable or disable Google Maps embed on Thank You page. Requires Google API key.'=>'在謝謝頁面啟用或停用 Google 地圖嵌入。需要 Google API 金鑰。','Enable Thank You Page Template For Viewing Orders in My Account'=>'啟用謝謝頁面範本以查看我的帳戶中的訂單','When checked, viewing orders in My Account will use the Thank You page template.'=>'勾選後，查看我的帳戶中的訂單將使用謝謝頁面範本。','Order Statuses'=>'訂單狀態','Choose which Order Statuses are shown as a progress bar on the Thank You page.'=>'選擇哪些訂單狀態會在謝謝頁面上顯示為進度條。','Icon Color'=>'圖示顏色','Heading above the suggested products. Leave blank for default. Default: You may also like&hellip;'=>'推薦商品上方的標題。留空則為預設。預設值：您可能也喜歡&hellip;','You may also like…'=>'您可能也喜歡…','Enable Random Cross Sells Fallback'=>'啟用隨機交叉銷售備用','If none of the cart products have cross sell items defined, display random products instead.'=>'如果購物車中的商品沒有定義交叉銷售商品，則改為顯示隨機商品。','Enable Floating Cart Button'=>'啟用浮動購物車按鈕','Enable floating cart button on the bottom right of pages.'=>'在頁面右下角啟用浮動購物車按鈕。','Right Position'=>'右側位置','The position from the right side of the screen in pixels. Default: 20'=>'距離螢幕右側的像素位置。預設值：20','Bottom Position'=>'底部位置','The position from the bottom of the screen in pixels. Default: 20'=>'距離螢幕底部的像素位置。預設值：20','Hide Button If Empty Cart'=>'購物車空時隱藏按鈕','Hide floating cart button if cart is empty.'=>'購物車空時隱藏浮動購物車按鈕。','Free Shipping Progress Bar'=>'免運費進度條','Configure the Free Shipping Progress Bar'=>'配置免運費進度條','Enable Free Shipping Progress Bar'=>'啟用免運費進度條','Enable Free Shipping progress bar to show customers how close they are to obtaining free shipping. Uses your shipping settings to determine limits. To override, specify amount below.'=>'啟用免運費進度條，向顧客顯示距離免運費還有多近。使用您的運費設定來判定門檻。若要覆蓋，請在下方指定金額。','Free Shipping Threshold'=>'免運費門檻','Cart subtotal required to qualify for free shipping. To use automatic detection based on shipping configuration, leave blank. Enter in store base currency.'=>'達到免運費資格所需的購物車小計。若要使用基於運費設定的自動偵測，請留空。請以商店基礎貨幣輸入。','Amount Remaining Message'=>'剩餘金額訊息','You\'re %s away from free shipping!'=>'您距離免費送貨還有 %s！','The amount remaining to qualify for free shipping message. Leave blank for default. Default: You\'re %s away from free shipping!'=>'符合免運條件的剩餘金額訊息。留空則使用預設值。預設值：您還差 %s 即可享免運！','Please ensure your amount remaining message includes the %s placeholder which is replaced with amount remaining when displayed to customers.'=>'請確保您的剩餘金額訊息包含 %s 佔位符，該佔位符會在顯示給顧客時被剩餘金額取代。','Free Shipping Message'=>'免運訊息','The free shipping message. Leave blank for default. Default: Congrats! You get free standard shipping.'=>'免運訊息。留空則使用預設值。預設值：恭喜！您可享有免費標準運送。','Enable Free Shipping Progress Bar At Checkout'=>'在結帳時啟用免運進度條','Enable Free Shipping Progress Bar on the checkout page cart summary.'=>'在結帳頁面的購物車摘要中啟用免運進度條。','Progress Indicator Color'=>'進度指示器顏色','Progress Bar Background Color'=>'進度條背景顏色','Options'=>'選項','Control various Side Cart options.'=>'控制各種側邊購物車選項。','Disable Cart Auto Open'=>'停用購物車自動開啟','Instead of opening the side cart, gently shake the floating cart button (if visible) to indicate a successful add to cart event.'=>'不開啟側邊購物車，而是輕微搖動浮動購物車按鈕（如果可見）以表示成功加入購物車事件。','Enable AJAX Add to Cart'=>'啟用 AJAX 加入購物車','Use AJAX on archive and single product pages to add items to cart. By default, WooCommerce requires a full form submit with page reload. Enabling this option uses AJAX to add items to the cart.'=>'在商品列表和單一商品頁面使用 AJAX 加入購物車。預設情況下，WooCommerce 需要完整表單提交並重新載入頁面。啟用此選項將使用 AJAX 加入購物車。','Enable Express Payment Buttons'=>'啟用快速付款按鈕','Enable express payment buttons from gateways that support the WooCommerce Minicart.'=>'啟用支援 WooCommerce 小購物車的支付閘道快速付款按鈕。','Enable order bumps that are set to display below cart items to appear in side cart.'=>'啟用設定為顯示於購物車商品下方的訂單加購，並在側邊購物車中顯示。','Allow Variation Changes'=>'允許變體變更','Displays an edit link under cart items that allows customers to change which variation is selected in the cart.'=>'在購物車商品下方顯示編輯連結，允許顧客更改購物車中選擇的變體。','Enable sale price under on cart item labels in side cart. Example: <s>$10.00</s> $5.00'=>'在側邊購物車的購物車商品標籤下方啟用促銷價格。範例：<s>$10.00</s> $5.00','Enable Coupons'=>'啟用優惠券','Enable customers to apply coupons from the side cart.'=>'允許顧客從側邊購物車套用優惠券。','Hide Coupon Code Field Behind Link'=>'將優惠券代碼欄位隱藏於連結後方','Initially hide coupon field until "Have a coupon code?" link is clicked.'=>'初始隱藏優惠券欄位，直到點擊「有優惠券代碼嗎？」連結。','Show Shipping and Totals'=>'顯示運費與總計','Enable customers to see shipping and order total in addition to subtotal.'=>'允許顧客查看運費與訂單總計，除了小計之外。','Enable Continue Shopping Button'=>'啟用繼續購物按鈕','Enable Continue Shopping Button at bottom of Side Cart. Disabled by default.'=>'在側邊購物車底部啟用繼續購物按鈕。預設為停用。','You probably do not want to select any pickup methods here. If you do not select any Local Pickup Shipping Methods, we will add an ad-hoc local pickup shipping method in each zone for you. If you would prefer to manage this yourself, you can select the methods you want to use here.'=>'您可能不想在此選擇任何取貨方式。如果您未選擇任何本地取貨運送方式，我們會在每個區域為您新增臨時的本地取貨運送方式。如果您想自行管理，您可以在此選擇想使用的方法。','Reasons You Might Want To Specify Your Own Pickup Methods:'=>'您可能想指定自訂取貨方式的原因：','You are charging for local pickup.'=>'您對本地取貨收費。','You want to use a custom local pickup method name.'=>'您想使用自訂的本地取貨方式名稱。','You have multiple local pickup options. (Not to be confused with locations. You should not use multiple local pickup methods for locations.)'=>'您有多個本地取貨選項。（不要與地點混淆。您不應該為地點使用多個本地取貨方式。）','Other Shipping Method'=>'其他運送方式','Enter the name of your local pickup shipping method. If you have multiple options, or the name varies, check the box below to use regular expressions.'=>'輸入您本地取貨運送方式的名稱。如果您有多個選項，或名稱有所不同，請勾選下方方框以使用正則表達式。','Enable Regex'=>'啟用正則表達式','Match local shipping method name with regex.'=>'使用正則表達式匹配本地運送方式名稱。','Configure Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA protection for your checkout and account pages.'=>'為您的結帳和帳戶頁面設定 Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA 保護。','Enable Cloudflare Turnstile'=>'啟用 Cloudflare Turnstile','Enable Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA protection'=>'啟用 Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA 保護','Site Key'=>'網站金鑰','Your Cloudflare Turnstile site key'=>'您的 Cloudflare Turnstile 網站金鑰','Secret Key'=>'密鑰','Your Cloudflare Turnstile secret key'=>'您的 Cloudflare Turnstile 密鑰','Enable on Checkout'=>'在結帳時啟用','Show Turnstile on the checkout page'=>'在結帳頁面顯示 Turnstile','Enable on Order Pay'=>'在訂單付款時啟用','Show Turnstile on the order pay page'=>'在訂單付款頁面顯示 Turnstile','Enable on Login'=>'在登入時啟用','Show Turnstile on the My Account login form'=>'在我的帳戶登入表單顯示 Turnstile','Enable on Registration'=>'在註冊時啟用','Show Turnstile on the My Account registration form'=>'在我的帳戶註冊表單顯示 Turnstile','Position on Checkout'=>'結帳頁面位置','Where to display the Turnstile widget on checkout'=>'在結帳頁面顯示 Turnstile 小工具的位置','Before Place Order Button'=>'下訂單按鈕之前','Display just before the place order button'=>'顯示於下訂單按鈕之前','Before Payment Methods'=>'付款方式之前','Display before payment method selection'=>'顯示於付款方式選擇之前','After Payment Methods'=>'付款方式之後','Display after payment method selection'=>'顯示於付款方式選擇之後','Theme'=>'主題','Visual theme for the Turnstile widget'=>'Turnstile 小工具的視覺主題','Light'=>'淺色','Light theme'=>'淺色主題','Dark'=>'深色','Dark theme'=>'深色主題','Auto'=>'自動','Automatic based on user preference'=>'根據使用者偏好自動調整','Size'=>'大小','Size of the Turnstile widget'=>'Turnstile 小工具的大小','Normal'=>'標準','Standard size widget'=>'標準大小的小工具','Compact'=>'緊湊','Smaller widget size'=>'較小的小工具大小','Guest Users Only'=>'僅限訪客使用者','Only show Turnstile for guest (non-logged-in) users'=>'僅對訪客（未登入）使用者顯示 Turnstile','Google API'=>'Google API','Used for the maps embed on the thank you page as well as Google Address Autocomplete.'=>'用於感謝頁面的地圖嵌入以及 Google 地址自動完成。','Google API Key'=>'Google API 金鑰','Used by Address Autocomplete and Thank You Page Maps Embed.'=>'用於地址自動完成和感謝頁面地圖嵌入。','Themes and Plugins'=>'主題與外掛','Integrations with 3rd party themes and plugins.'=>'與第三方主題和外掛的整合。','Control express checkout options.'=>'控制快速結帳選項。','Disable Express Checkout'=>'停用快速結帳','Prevent Express Checkout options from loading, such as Apple Pay and PayPal. <a href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/" target="_blank" class="ml-1 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Learn More</a>'=>'防止快速結帳選項載入，例如 Apple Pay 和 PayPal。<a href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/" target="_blank" class="ml-1 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">了解更多</a>','Detected Gateways'=>'偵測到的支付閘道','Gateway'=>'支付閘道','Express Checkout Support'=>'快速結帳支援','Recommendation'=>'建議','No supported gateways detected. <a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" target="_blank" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/">See our recommended Express Checkout gateways here.</a>'=>'未偵測到支援的支付閘道。<a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" target="_blank" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/">請參閱我們推薦的快速結帳支付閘道。</a>','Steps'=>'步驟','Control the checkout steps.'=>'控制結帳步驟。','Disable Cart Step'=>'停用購物車步驟','Disable to skip the cart and redirect customers directly to checkout after adding a product to the cart. (Incompatible with Side Cart)'=>'停用後，加入商品至購物車後會直接跳過購物車並導向結帳頁面。（與側邊購物車不相容）','Disable Shipping Step'=>'停用運送步驟','Disable to hide the shipping method step. Useful if you only have one shipping option for all orders.'=>'停用後隱藏運送方式步驟。如果所有訂單只有一種運送選項，這功能很有用。','Enable Order Review Step'=>'啟用訂單審核步驟','Adds a review step after payment information before finalizing order. Useful for jurisdictions which require additional confirmation before order submission. (Cannot be used with One Page Checkout)'=>'在付款資訊後、完成訂單前新增審核步驟。適用於需要額外確認才能提交訂單的法域。（無法與單頁結帳同時使用）','Enable One Page Checkout'=>'啟用單頁結帳','Show all checkout steps on  one page. Useful for digital stores. (Cannot be used with Order Review Step)'=>'在同一頁面顯示所有結帳步驟。適用於數位商店。（無法與訂單審核步驟同時使用）','Shipping Options'=>'運送選項','Control shipping options.'=>'控制運送選項。','Auto Select Free Shipping Method (if available)'=>'自動選擇免費運送方式（若可用）','WooCommerce has a habit of not selecting the free shipping method if it is setup to be conditionally enabled. This option auto-selects the free shipping on page load.'=>'WooCommerce 若設定條件啟用免費運送，通常不會自動選擇此方式。此選項會在頁面載入時自動選擇免費運送。','Login and Registration'=>'登入與註冊','Control how login and registration function on your checkout page.'=>'控制結帳頁面上的登入與註冊功能。','Disable Automatic Login Modal'=>'停用自動登入彈窗','Normally the login modal automatically opens if the entered email address matches an existing account. This disables that behavior.'=>'通常輸入的電子郵件地址符合現有帳號時，登入彈窗會自動開啟。此選項停用該行為。','Registration'=>'註冊','Choose how customers obtain a password when registering an account.'=>'選擇客戶註冊帳號時如何取得密碼。','Enhanced (Recommended)'=>'增強（建議）','Automatically generate a username and password and email it to the customer using the native WooCommerce functionality. (Recommended)'=>'自動產生使用者名稱與密碼，並使用 WooCommerce 原生功能寄送給客戶。（建議）','A password field is provided for the customer to select their own password. Not recommended.'=>'提供密碼欄位讓客戶自行設定密碼。不建議使用。','User Matching'=>'使用者匹配','Choose how to handle guest orders and accounts.'=>'選擇如何處理訪客訂單與帳號。','Enabled (Recommended)'=>'啟用（建議）','Automatically matches guest orders to user accounts on new purchase as well as on registration of a new user. (Recommended)'=>'在新購買及新使用者註冊時，自動將訪客訂單匹配至使用者帳號。（建議）','Guest orders will not be linked to matching accounts.'=>'訪客訂單不會連結至匹配的帳號。','Field Options'=>'欄位選項','Control how different checkout fields appear.'=>'控制不同結帳欄位的顯示方式。','Phone Field'=>'電話欄位','Determines whether the WooCommerce native phone field is enabled.'=>'決定是否啟用 WooCommerce 原生電話欄位。','Hidden'=>'隱藏','Optional'=>'選填','Required'=>'必填','Enable Order Notes Field'=>'啟用訂單備註欄位','Enable or disable WooCommerce Order Notes field. (Default: Disabled)'=>'啟用或停用 WooCommerce 訂單備註欄位。（預設：停用）','Order Notes field is being controlled by a filter or a plugin.'=>'訂單備註欄位由過濾器或外掛控制中。','Hide Optional Address Fields Behind Links'=>'將可選地址欄位隱藏在連結後面','Recommended to increase conversions. Example link text: Add Company (optional)'=>'建議提高轉換率。範例連結文字：新增公司（可選）','Disable Email Domain Autocomplete'=>'停用電子郵件網域自動完成','Disable email domain autocomplete.'=>'停用電子郵件網域自動完成。','Enable Separate House Number and Street Name Address Fields'=>'啟用分開的門牌號碼和街道名稱地址欄位','Values are combined into a single address_1 field based on country selected by customer.'=>'根據客戶選擇的國家，將值合併為單一的 address_1 欄位。','Separate Address Fields Display Order'=>'分開地址欄位顯示順序','Choose how display separate address 1 fields.'=>'選擇如何顯示分開的 address 1 欄位。','[House Number] [Street Name]'=>'[門牌號碼] [街道名稱]','Display the House Number before the Street Name. (Default)'=>'在街道名稱前顯示門牌號碼。（預設）','[Street Name] [House Number]'=>'[街道名稱] [門牌號碼]','Display the Street Name before the House Number.'=>'在門牌號碼前顯示街道名稱。','Separate Address Fields is incompatible with Google Address Autocomplete. <a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">Learn More</a>'=>'分開地址欄位與 Google 地址自動完成不相容。<a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">了解更多</a>','Enable Full Name Field'=>'啟用全名欄位','Enable to replace first and last name fields with a single full name field.'=>'啟用以用單一全名欄位取代名字和姓氏欄位。','Enable Highlighted Countries'=>'啟用突出顯示國家','Promote selected countries to the top of the countries list in country dropdowns.'=>'將選定的國家提升至國家下拉選單列表頂端。','Highlighted Countries'=>'突出顯示的國家','The countries to show first in country dropdowns.'=>'在國家下拉選單中優先顯示的國家。','Enable International Phone Field'=>'啟用國際電話欄位','Validate phone number entry based on selected country. Replaces phone field placeholder with example phone number. Stores phone number according to International Phone Format.'=>'根據選擇的國家驗證電話號碼輸入。用範例電話號碼取代電話欄位的提示文字。依國際電話格式儲存電話號碼。','International Phone Format'=>'國際電話格式','Choose how to store phone numbers.'=>'選擇如何儲存電話號碼。','Raw Value (No Formatting)'=>'原始值（無格式）','The number is stored exactly how the user entered it.'=>'號碼將以使用者輸入的原始形式儲存。','E164'=>'E164','Format phone number with E164 standard.'=>'以 E164 標準格式化電話號碼。','International'=>'國際格式','Format phone number with RFC3966 standard without the tel: prefix'=>'以 RFC3966 標準格式化電話號碼，無 tel: 前綴','National'=>'國內格式','Format phone number based on selected country. US Example (555) 555 - 5555, UK Example: 07911 123457'=>'根據選擇的國家格式化電話號碼。美國範例 (555) 555 - 5555，英國範例：07911 123457','RFC3966'=>'RFC3966','Format phone number with RFC3966 standard.'=>'以 RFC3966 標準格式化電話號碼。','Address Options'=>'地址選項','Control address fields.'=>'控制地址欄位。','Force Different Billing Address'=>'強制不同的帳單地址','Remove option to use shipping address as billing address.'=>'移除使用運送地址作為帳單地址的選項。','Hide Billing Address For Free Orders'=>'免費訂單隱藏帳單地址','Remove the billing address fields from checkout for free orders.'=>'在結帳時移除免費訂單的帳單地址欄位。','Enabled Billing Address Fields'=>'啟用的帳單地址欄位','Choose which billing address fields are visible for customers.'=>'選擇哪些帳單地址欄位對客戶可見。','First Name'=>'名字','Last Name'=>'姓氏','Address 1'=>'地址 1','Address 2'=>'地址 2','Company'=>'公司','Country'=>'國家','Postcode'=>'郵遞區號','State'=>'州/省','City'=>'城市','Disabling the country or state field causes issues with some gateways. Consider leaving these fields enabled.'=>'停用國家或州欄位會導致某些支付閘道出現問題。建議保留這些欄位啟用。','Address Completion and Validation'=>'地址補全與驗證','Control some mobile only checkout behaviors.'=>'控制部分僅限行動裝置的結帳行為。','Enable Google Address Autocomplete'=>'啟用 Google 地址自動完成','Google Address Autocomplete cannot be used with Separate Address Fields. <a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">Learn More</a>'=>'Google 地址自動完成無法與分開地址欄位一起使用。<a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">了解更多</a>','Enable Fetchify Address Autocomplete'=>'啟用 Fetchify 地址自動完成','Enable or disable Fetchify address autocomplete feature. <a href="https://fetchify.com" class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank">Requires Fetchify access token.</a>'=>'啟用或停用 Fetchify 地址自動完成功能。<a href="https://fetchify.com" class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank">需要 Fetchify 存取權杖。</a>','Fetchify Access Token'=>'Fetchify 存取權杖','Your Fetchify access token.'=>'您的 Fetchify 存取權杖。','You can only use one address autocomplete service at a time. Please disable one of the services.'=>'您一次只能使用一個地址自動完成服務。請停用其中一項服務。','Enable Smarty Address Validation'=>'啟用 Smarty 地址驗證','Validates shipping address with Smarty.com and provides alternative, corrected addresses for incorrect or incomplete addresses.'=>'使用 Smarty.com 驗證送貨地址，並為不正確或不完整的地址提供替代且修正的地址。','Smarty Auth ID'=>'Smarty 認證 ID','Smarty Auth ID. Available in your <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty Account</a>'=>'Smarty 認證 ID。可在您的 <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty 帳戶</a> 中取得','Smarty Auth Token'=>'Smarty 認證權杖','Smarty Auth Token. Available in your <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty Account</a>.'=>'Smarty 認證權杖。可在您的 <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty 帳戶</a> 中取得。','Enable Cart Editing At Checkout'=>'啟用結帳時購物車編輯','Enable or disable Cart Editing. Allows customer to remove or adjust quantity of cart items at checkout.'=>'啟用或停用購物車編輯。允許客戶在結帳時移除或調整購物車商品數量。','Show Item Remove Button'=>'顯示商品移除按鈕','When hovering over an item, show a button (X) to remove the item.'=>'當滑鼠移至商品上方時，顯示一個按鈕 (X) 以移除該商品。','Cart Editing Empty Cart Redirect'=>'購物車編輯空購物車重定向','URL to redirect to when customer empties cart from checkout page. If left blank, customer will be redirected to the cart page.'=>'當客戶從結帳頁面清空購物車時的重定向網址。若留空，客戶將被重定向至購物車頁面。','Enable Sticky Cart Summary'=>'啟用固定購物車摘要','If cart summary is shorter than the rest of the content, it will stick to the top of the screen when scrolling.'=>'如果購物車摘要比其他內容短，捲動時它會固定在畫面頂端。','Mobile Options'=>'行動裝置選項','Control mobile specific features.'=>'控制行動裝置專屬功能。','Enable Mobile Cart Summary'=>'啟用行動購物車摘要','Shows the cart, promo field, and totals at the bottom of the first checkout step.'=>'在結帳的第一步底部顯示購物車、促銷欄位和總計。','Enable Mobile Totals'=>'啟用行動總計','Shows cart totals right above the place order button on mobile.'=>'在行動裝置上於下訂單按鈕上方顯示購物車總計。','Enable Mobile Coupon Field'=>'啟用行動優惠券欄位','Show coupon field above payment gateways on mobile devices. Helps customers find the coupon field without expanding the cart summary.'=>'在行動裝置上於付款閘道上方顯示優惠券欄位。幫助顧客在不展開購物車摘要的情況下找到優惠券欄位。','Enable Mobile Cart Summary is not compatible with Enable Mobile Coupon Field. Please disable one of the options.'=>'啟用行動購物車摘要與啟用行動優惠券欄位不相容。請停用其中一個選項。','Enable Mobile Credit Card Logos'=>'啟用行動信用卡標誌','Show the credit card logos on mobile. Note: Many gateway logos cannot be rendered properly on mobile. It is recommended you test before enabling. Default: Off'=>'在行動裝置上顯示信用卡標誌。注意：許多閘道標誌無法在行動裝置上正確呈現。建議啟用前先測試。預設：關閉','Cart Summary Mobile Label'=>'購物車摘要行動標籤','Example: Show order summary and coupons. If left blank, this default will be used: Show order summary'=>'範例：顯示訂單摘要和優惠券。若留空，將使用此預設值：顯示訂單摘要','Order Pay'=>'訂單付款','Enable CheckoutWC template for the Order Pay / Customer Payment Page endpoint.'=>'為訂單付款 / 客戶付款頁面端點啟用 CheckoutWC 範本。','Enable Order Pay Page'=>'啟用訂單付款頁面','Use CheckoutWC templates for Order Pay page.'=>'訂單付款頁面使用 CheckoutWC 範本。','General Template Settings'=>'一般範本設定','Configure your template.'=>'設定您的範本。','Logo'=>'標誌','Choose the logo you wish to display in the header. If you do not choose a logo we will use your site name.'=>'選擇您想在標頭顯示的標誌。若未選擇標誌，我們將使用您的網站名稱。','Field Label Style'=>'欄位標籤樣式','Choose how you want form labels styled.'=>'選擇您想要的表單標籤樣式。','Floating (Recommended)'=>'浮動（建議）','Automatically show and hide labels based on whether the field has a value. (Recommended)'=>'根據欄位是否有值，自動顯示和隱藏標籤。（建議）','Labels appear above each field at all times.'=>'標籤始終顯示在每個欄位上方。','Typography'=>'字體排印','Configure fonts.'=>'設定字體。','Body Font'=>'正文字體','Choose the font for the body text.'=>'選擇正文字體。','Heading Font'=>'標題字體','Choose the font for the headings.'=>'選擇標題字體。','Colors'=>'顏色','Configure template colors.'=>'設定範本顏色。','CSS'=>'CSS','Customize template CSS.'=>'自訂範本 CSS。','Custom CSS'=>'自訂 CSS','Add Custom CSS rules to fully control the appearance of the checkout template.'=>'新增自訂 CSS 規則以完全控制結帳範本的外觀。','Experimental Options'=>'實驗性選項','These options are not fully supported and may require a developer to implement successfully.'=>'這些選項尚未完全支援，可能需要開發人員協助成功實作。','Template Loader'=>'範本載入器','Choose how to load the templates. (Checkout, Order Pay, Thank You)'=>'選擇如何載入範本。（結帳、訂單付款、感謝頁）','Distraction Free Portal (Recommended)'=>'無干擾入口（建議）','Display CheckoutWC templates in a distraction free portal which does not load the active WordPress theme or styles. (Recommended)'=>'在無干擾入口中顯示 CheckoutWC 範本，不載入啟用中的 WordPress 主題或樣式。（建議）','WordPress Theme'=>'WordPress 主題','Load CheckoutWC templates within active WordPress theme content area. (<span style="color:red">Unsupported Configuration</span>)'=>'在啟用中的 WordPress 主題內容區域載入 CheckoutWC 範本。(<span style="color:red">不支援的設定</span>)','Using this option renders our templates inside of your theme content area. This may cause conflicts with your theme\'s stylesheets and scripts. Please note, resolving any issues that arise from this loader will be your responsibility.'=>'使用此選項會將我們的範本呈現在您的主題內容區域內。這可能會導致與您的主題樣式表和腳本發生衝突。請注意，解決由此載入器引起的任何問題將由您自行負責。','Enable Beta Version Updates'=>'啟用 Beta 版本更新','Allows automatic updates to the latest beta version.'=>'允許自動更新至最新的 Beta 版本。','Delete Plugin Data on Uninstall'=>'卸載時刪除外掛資料','If you want a fresh start.'=>'如果您想重新開始。','We are great at categorizing things!'=>'我們擅長分類事物！','Hide Admin Menu Bar Button'=>'隱藏管理選單列按鈕','Hide the CheckoutWC admin menu bar button unless you are on the checkout page, or one of the checkout endpoints such as thank you and order pay.'=>'除非您在結帳頁面或結帳端點（例如感謝頁和訂單付款頁），否則隱藏 CheckoutWC 管理選單列按鈕。','Enable Debug Log'=>'啟用除錯日誌','Logs debug information to WP Admin > WooCommerce > Status > Logs > checkout-wc-*.log'=>'將除錯資訊記錄到 WP 管理 > WooCommerce > 狀態 > 日誌 > checkout-wc-*.log','Enable Usage Tracking'=>'啟用使用追蹤','Allow CheckoutWC to track plugin usage.'=>'允許 CheckoutWC 追蹤外掛使用情況。','Global'=>'全域','Add custom scripts that run on all enabled CheckoutWC templates. (Checkout, Thank You, Order Pay)'=>'新增會在所有啟用的 CheckoutWC 範本（結帳、感謝頁、訂單付款）上執行的自訂腳本。','Header Scripts'=>'頁首腳本','This code will output immediately before the closing <code>&lt;/head&gt;</code> tag in the document source.'=>'此程式碼將在文件原始碼中 <code>&lt;/head&gt;</code> 標籤關閉前立即輸出。','Footer Scripts'=>'頁尾腳本','This code will output immediately before the closing <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> tag in the document source.'=>'此程式碼將在文件原始碼中 <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> 標籤關閉前立即輸出。','Header and Footer Scripts are HTML only. For PHP, use PHP Snippets option.'=>'頁首和頁尾腳本僅限 HTML。PHP 請使用 PHP 片段選項。','PHP Snippets'=>'PHP 片段','Add PHP snippets to modify your checkout page here. If you have lots of snippets, you may want to consider using <a class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank" href="%s">Code Snippets</a>.'=>'在此新增 PHP 片段以修改您的結帳頁面。如果您有大量片段，建議考慮使用 <a class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank" href="%s">Code Snippets</a>。','Please omit the opening PHP tag.'=>'請省略開頭的 PHP 標籤。','Add custom JavaScript and PHP that runs on the checkout page.'=>'新增會在結帳頁面執行的自訂 JavaScript 和 PHP。','Add custom JavaScript and PHP that runs on the Order Received / Thank You page.'=>'新增會在訂單完成／感謝頁執行的自訂 JavaScript 和 PHP。','Add custom JavaScript and PHP that runs on the Order Pay page.'=>'新增會在訂單付款頁執行的自訂 JavaScript 和 PHP。','Exclude From Abandoned Cart Recovery By Role'=>'依角色排除放棄購物車回復','Check any user role that should be excluded from abandoned cart emails.'=>'勾選任何應排除於放棄購物車電子郵件之外的使用者角色。','Are you sure you want to delete all tracked carts?'=>'您確定要刪除所有追蹤的購物車嗎？','Is equal to'=>'等于','Is not equal to'=>'不等于','Is greater than'=>'大于','Is less than'=>'小于','Is greater or equal to'=>'大于或等于','Is less than or equal to'=>'小于或等于','Was placed on'=>'被置于','Was not placed on'=>'未列入','Was placed after'=>'是在','Was placed before'=>'被置于','On'=>'关于','Not on'=>'不在','After'=>'之后','Before'=>'之前','At least one of the selected'=>'至少一个选定的','All of the selected'=>'所有选定的','None of the selected'=>'所选','Select Condition…'=>'选择条件...','Select Order Type…'=>'选择订单类型...','Select Product Category…'=>'选择产品类别...','Select Product Tag…'=>'选择产品标签...','Select Product…'=>'选择产品...','Select Inventory Status…'=>'选择库存状态...','Select User Role…'=>'选择用户角色...','Cart Contents'=>'购物车内容','Is empty'=>'是空的','Is not empty'=>'不为空','Contains (Products)'=>'包含（产品）','Contains (Categories)'=>'包含（类别）','Contains (Tags)'=>'包含（标签）','Cart Total Quantity'=>'购物车总数量','Cart Subtotal'=>'购物车小计','Quantity of Product in Cart'=>'购物车中的产品数量','Quantity of Category in Cart'=>'购物车中的类别数量','Cart Coupons'=>'购物车优惠券','Has no coupon'=>'没有优惠券','Has coupon'=>'有优惠券','Enter coupon codes...'=>'输入优惠券代码...','Customer History: Total Spent'=>'客户历史：消费总额','Customer History: Average Order Value'=>'客户历史：平均订单价值','Customer History: Total Orders'=>'客户历史：订单总数','Customer History: Quantity of Product Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购产品数量','Customer History: Quantity of Category Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购的类别数量','Customer History: Time Since Order'=>'客户历史：订购后的时间','First order'=>'一阶','Last order'=>'最后订单','Customer History: Time Since Product Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购产品后的时间','Customer History: Time Since Category Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购类别后的时间','Customer History: Date of Order'=>'客户历史：订购日期','Customer History: Date of Product Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购产品日期','First ordered'=>'首次订购','Last ordered'=>'最后订购','Customer History: Date of Category Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购类别日期','Product Inventory'=>'产品库存','Is in stock'=>'有库存','Is out of stock'=>'缺货','Is on backorder'=>'正在延期交货','Quantity of Product in Stock'=>'库存产品数量','Shipping Country'=>'航运国家','Billing Country'=>'账单国家','Add rule'=>'新增規則','Show If'=>'顯示條件','And If'=>'且條件','Delete Rule'=>'刪除規則','woocommerceShipping'=>'运输','full stringSuffix'=>'后缀']];